{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The purpose of this field is to synchronize transitions initiated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by sending the same message multiple times with a short delay."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a Node would want to send a Generic On Off Set"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Unacknowledged message to a Group Address. In order to increase"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of successful delivery, such message can be repeated."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The first message could be sent with longer "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and each following with a shorter one, so when different Nodes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"receive different messages, the action they take seems more","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"synchronized.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This file has to be set together with ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/transitionTime","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSet\/delay"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslset\/delay"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSet"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delay"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8"},{"kind":"text","text":"?"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"delay","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh11LightHSLSetV5delays5UInt8VSgvp"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/LightHSLSet/delay":{"fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delay","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"},{"text":"?","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/LightHSLSet\/delay","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/lighthslset\/delay","title":"delay","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Message execution delay in 5 millisecond steps.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/TransitionMessage/delay":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/TransitionMessage\/delay","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/transitionmessage\/delay","abstract":[{"type":"text","t